name: KITSUNE FOX
description:
In the Japanese language, kitsune can mean both a regular Japanese fox, a divine fox, or a demon fox.Japanese kitsune are shapeshifters. The older a kitsune gets, the more its abilities increase. It is said that when a Japanese fox turns 100 years old, it can turn into a human.

Modeled and animated in C4d, textured in substance painter, other details animated in AfterEffects.
